751
00:39:02,507 --> 00:39:04,440
<i>when all you want is your bed.</i>

752
00:39:05,610 --> 00:39:08,578
<i>So... how do you keep going?</i>

753
00:39:11,783 --> 00:39:14,184
<i>How do you not just
